    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款多人FPS射击游戏，具有多种游戏模式。你必须用你的声音才能看到其他玩家，否则你只能看到黑暗。只有当你声音很大时，你的武器才能发挥作用。仅当麦克风打开时您才能玩此游戏。语音聊天保证!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>静音 =&gt; 隐形</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324800/extras/336ab4a685e319e56d15589ded702c3c.poster.avif?t=1732274756\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324800/extras/336ab4a685e319e56d15589ded702c3c.webm?t=1732274756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你不发出声音，其他玩家就看不到你。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当您跑步时，他们只能看到/听到您的脚步声。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>喊叫 =&gt; 看到并射击</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324800/extras/1cfd9f8fbc5c12734d0660316906661a.poster.avif?t=1732274756\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324800/extras/1cfd9f8fbc5c12734d0660316906661a.webm?t=1732274756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你发出声音，就会产生声波。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过声波，你可以看到周围的环境，也可以看到其他玩家的轮廓。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >声音越大，看得越远。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以用麦克风发出声音。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>更大声 =&gt; 更好</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324800/extras/49be1b0cc98f541b73069006efe23616.poster.avif?t=1732274756\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324800/extras/49be1b0cc98f541b73069006efe23616.webm?t=1732274756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324800/extras/49be1b0cc98f541b73069006efe23616.mp4?t=1732274756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有枪支都有一个音量阈值，您必须达到该阈值才能使用它进行射击。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的声音越大，你的武器就越准确。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多人游戏</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >语音聊天</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多张地图</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种独特的声控武器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种游戏模式：大逃杀、PVP、TDM、夺旗、捉迷藏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可定制的角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无微交易</p></li></ul>",
